== Yang Water Tiger Month ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦}} year whose last digit is 2 or 7 (when the Heavenly Stem is {{ill|Ren|ja|壬}} or {{ill|Ding|ja|丁}}), the month of {{ill|January|ja|1月}} is considered the Yang Water Tiger {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}}. However, the month referred to here may also be based on the {{ill|Old Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Old Lunar Calendar}} or on the seasonal month (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|立春}} to the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|啓蟄}}).

== Yang Water Tiger Day ==
=== Selected Day ===
The Yang Water Tiger day is the 10th day of {{ill|Tian Yi Tianshang|ja|天一天上}}.

