== Yang Water Tiger Month ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} year whose last digit is 2 or 7 (when the Heavenly Stem is {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Ding|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|January|ja|1月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is considered the Yang Water Tiger {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. However, the month referred to here may also be based on the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or on the seasonal month (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|立春|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|啓蟄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}).

== Yang Water Tiger Day ==
=== Selected Day ===
