== Yang Water Tiger Month ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose last digit is 2 or 7 (when the Heavenly Stem is {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=}} or {{ill|Ding|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ding|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|January|ja|1月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January|qq=}} is considered the Yang Water Tiger {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}}. However, the month referred to here may also be based on the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or on the seasonal month (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|立春|1=Lichun|lt=Risshun|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Risshun|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|啓蟄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichitsu|qq=}}).

== Yang Water Tiger Day ==
=== Selected Day ===
The Yang Water Tiger day is the 10th day of {{ill|Tian Yi Tianshang|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tian Yi Tianshang|qq=}}.
